{"tid":1948654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[陰毛論] [真點最大贏家] 有冇人諗過最後可能係中共統治全世界","createTime":"2020-03-29T07:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T07:35:51.000Z","uid":39218,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"891df0a8f2f043fb63c61e89504763066705dbbd","tid":1948654,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:05:06.000Z","msg":"以下全部都係我自己嘅假設<br />\n如有雷同實屬巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻毒係中共整出黎嘅人工病毒就係人都知<br />\n而目的就係削減全世界人口<br />\n咁梗係要自己國內爆左先啦<br />\n唔係就企圖太明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你又會見到啲高官政要全部冇事<br />\n其他國家嘅達官貴人已經相繼染病甚至死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中蟈甚至香港嘅嗰堆冚家剷反而一啲事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就自然諗既然整得隻毒出黎<br />\n整埋抗體有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日美軍都開始有確診個案<br />\n再咁落去個局勢係非常唔明朗<br />\n全世界染病嘅時候要打仗就變左中共佔優<br />\n<br />\n唔通真係俾中共一隻病毒搞到冚球剷<br />\n成最後大贏家統治全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係home office冇野做屎忽痕鳩諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1043384fed87f804ec6255d35e5649c0c790048d","tid":1948654,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d475511cf502f4c0eec3533123e352e5c57c4f8f","tid":1948654,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人有其他諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af89d3ae778cebb2d17f0c370056a77d263589ab","tid":1948654,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"定係連登已經唔再係討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\